### Forward <up>
"mpc seek +00:00:10"
	m:0x0 + c:111

### Stop <backspace>
"mpc stop"
	m:0x0 + c:22

### Previous <left>
"mpc prev"
	m:0x0 + c:113

### Play / Pause <enter>
"mpc toggle"
	m:0x0 + c:36

### Next <right>
"mpc next"
	m:0x0 + c:114

